        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Allowing Body Cameras in Joint Task Forces Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill bars a federal prohibition on the use or wearing of body cameras by state or local law enforcement officers during joint operations with federal law enforcement officers.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
